@startuml Course State Machine
left to right direction

[*] --> PENDING_APPROVAL : Create course

PENDING_APPROVAL --> APPROVED : Admin approves
PENDING_APPROVAL --> REJECTED : Admin rejects

APPROVED --> READY_OPENED : Prepare course

READY_OPENED --> ON_GOING : Enrollment starts
READY_OPENED --> CANCELLED : Cancel before start

ON_GOING --> FULL : Max participants reached
ON_GOING --> COMPLETED : All sessions done
ON_GOING --> CANCELLED : Cancel after start

FULL --> ON_GOING : Participant dropped

REJECTED --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]
COMPLETED --> [*]

@enduml
